rComments: Chuck made it easy to learn chemistry and made it interesting too. You can always reach him and he is very helpful...class is inherently difficult, but the effort pays off.

Great TA. the class was not easy, but it wasnt his fault. he made really hard quizzes (they are curved so it doesnt matter) to prepare his students for the tests. after taking a class w/ chuck you know chemistry.  If you ever need to meet w/ him he will always make time to meet. he always sends emails keeping you on top of new things happening.
